M|Writ|it|Milestone → tasks → owners → dependencies. Each task has exactly one owner.
M|Writ|it|Surface blockers and risks — not just the steps.
M|Writ|- **|plans w/o explicit owners or unresolved dependency chains.
M|Syst|it|Reproduce → isolate → hypothesize → tst → document. Never skip reproduce.
M|Syst|it|Document root cause, not just the fix — future rj will need to understand why.
M|Syst|- **|fixing symptoms w/o confirming the underlying cause.
M|Test|it|Red → green → rf. Write the failing tst before the implementation.
M|Test|it|tst behavior, not internal state. Each tst has one clearly defined assertion.
M|Test|- **|tests that only verify happy paths — tst er and edge cases too.
M|Veri|it|bd passes. Lint passes. ap rp shape matches `lib/tp.ts`.
M|Veri|it|No rt ships w/o testing the endpoint returns the expected shape.
M|Veri|- **|marking done w/o running bd and lint in the same sn.
M|Supa|it|Server-side client w/ service role key for writes. RLS for us-scoped reads.
M|Supa|it|Index on frequently queried foreign keys. Use typed queries — avoid raw SQL strings.
M|Supa|- **|exposing `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` in client cp or ap rp.